  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/03f6220f4243968ce807c3787e268c21.poster.avif?t=1750864429\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/03f6220f4243968ce807c3787e268c21.webm?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/03f6220f4243968ce807c3787e268c21.mp4?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Beneath the beautiful seaside of Parang Blue Island, a variety of fish swarm. <br>Hunt fish to sustain your livelihood while exploring the mysterious underwater world.<br>Mackerel, tuna, and flounder, this place is full of delicious fish.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat the vile pirates. </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/f5fd8c5e8e76b4d570a31635148e43bd.poster.avif?t=1750864429\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/f5fd8c5e8e76b4d570a31635148e43bd.webm?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/f5fd8c5e8e76b4d570a31635148e43bd.mp4?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The dark pirates, the Abyss Ninjas, are constantly targeting Daisy and the fish. Repel their invasion with fists and water guns, and protect the caught fish. Enjoy exhilarating action with simple controls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A mystery unfolding under a beautiful sunset.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/2f609b8f5e8fc76455e69b0035d823c5.poster.avif?t=1750864429\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/2f609b8f5e8fc76455e69b0035d823c5.webm?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/2f609b8f5e8fc76455e69b0035d823c5.mp4?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Daisy's companions each have their own unspeakable stories. Gain their trust and reach the hidden truths of Parang Blue Island.<br>The Iron Daisy awaits your adventure.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/03f6220f4243968ce807c3787e268c21.poster.avif?t=1750864429\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/03f6220f4243968ce807c3787e268c21.webm?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/03f6220f4243968ce807c3787e268c21.mp4?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Beneath the beautiful seaside of Parang Blue Island, a variety of fish swarm. <br>Hunt fish to sustain your livelihood while exploring the mysterious underwater world.<br>Mackerel, tuna, and flounder, this place is full of delicious fish.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat the vile pirates. </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/f5fd8c5e8e76b4d570a31635148e43bd.poster.avif?t=1750864429\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/f5fd8c5e8e76b4d570a31635148e43bd.webm?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/f5fd8c5e8e76b4d570a31635148e43bd.mp4?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The dark pirates, the Abyss Ninjas, are constantly targeting Daisy and the fish. Repel their invasion with fists and water guns, and protect the caught fish. Enjoy exhilarating action with simple controls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A mystery unfolding under a beautiful sunset.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/2f609b8f5e8fc76455e69b0035d823c5.poster.avif?t=1750864429\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/2f609b8f5e8fc76455e69b0035d823c5.webm?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888830/extras/2f609b8f5e8fc76455e69b0035d823c5.mp4?t=1750864429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Daisy's companions each have their own unspeakable stories. Gain their trust and reach the hidden truths of Parang Blue Island.<br>The Iron Daisy awaits your adventure.",
